Class OhAccountDetails

java.lang.Object
  com.ryanantkowiak.jOptionsHouseAPI.IOh
      com.ryanantkowiak.jOptionsHouseAPI.OhAccountDetails

public class OhAccountDetails
extends IOh

This class will retrieve the Account Details from OptionsHouse. Account details include things such as: margin equity, account value, buying power, etc.

Author:
Ryan Antkowiak
